nhc_headline: ...HENRIETTE WEAKENING OVER THE CENTRAL NORTH PACIFIC...
summary: ...HENRIETTE WEAKENING OVER THE CENTRAL NORTH PACIFIC... As of 5:00 AM HST Tue Aug 12 the center of Henriette was located near 32.8, -161.6 with movement NW at 16 mph. The minimum central pressure was 994 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 70 mph.
